


Install in Ubuntu 14.04


Required libs
sudo apt-get install g++ m4 libqt4-dev libqt4-core libqt4-gui libqt4-opengl libqt4-network flex libxt-dev libsm-dev libxi-dev libaudio-dev libglib2.0-dev libxt-dev libxrender-dev libfreetype6-dev libfontconfig1-dev libboost-dev libboost-filesystem-dev libboost-system-dev libboost-program-options-dev


Download bison-2.7.tar.gz
    $ ./configure
    $ make
    $ sudo make install

Server
    tar zxf rcssserver-15.2.2.tar.gz
    ./configure --with-boost-system=boost_system --with-boost-filesystem=boost_filesystem
    make
    sudo make install



Monitor
    ./configure --with-boost-system=boost_system --with-boost-program-options=boost_program_options
    make
    sudo make install